flowchart TB
    Internet --> CDN[CDN/WAF]
    CDN --> LB[Load Balancer]
    LB --> Nginx[Nginx / Ingress]
    Nginx --> FE[Frontend Replicas]
    Nginx --> API[API Replicas]
    API --> Workers[Worker Pool]
    FE --> API
    API --> Cache[Redis Cache]
    API --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    Workers --> DB
    Workers --> ObjectStorage[(S3/GCS/Azure Blob/MinIO)]
    API --> Metrics[Prometheus]
    FE --> Logs[Central Logs/Sentry]
    API --> Logs
    Workers --> Logs
